在《最终幻想VII》中，与爱丽丝相关的主旋律播放了数次，在爱丽丝的母亲在她家中的倒叙场景中首次听到，并在她被萨菲罗斯杀死时重复。它由《最终幻想》作曲家[[植松伸夫|植松伸夫]]编曲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy Symphony :: Vocalists|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015035847/http://www.ffsymphony.net/vocalists.php|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2007-10-15|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>“在教堂裡盛开的花朵”（Flowers Blooming in the Church）片段也是基于此创作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=RPGFan Music - Final Fantasy VII OST|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/ff7ost/index.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.rpgfan.com|archive-date=2013-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116214810/http://rpgfan.com/soundtracks/ff7ost/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《爱丽丝主题曲》在最终幻想的粉丝中非常受欢迎，并启发了管弦乐版本、钢琴版本和由歌手中野律紀（她也为《最终幻想X》演唱过《{{lang|ja|素敵だね?}}》）演唱的人声版本。主题曲的钢琴版在《降临之子》中出现了两次，曲目《水》呼应了主题曲的另一面：爱丽丝主题曲的开头部分出现在曲目《Divinity II》的高潮之前，其后不久作为拉丁短语“ Sola Dea fatum novit”（“只有女神才知道命运”）的最后收束，并且在影片的尾声中也有所体现。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Game Music :: Final Fantasy VII Advent Children Original Soundtrack :: Album Information|url=https://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/f/ff7advent.shtml|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.squareenixmusic.com|archive-date=2019-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915225238/https://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/f/ff7advent.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>OverClocked ReMix 在《最终幻想VII》的相关作品《Voices of the Lifestream》（《生命之流的声音》）中进行了重新演绎。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tracks - Final Fantasy VII: Voices of the Lifestream, An OverClocked ReMix Album|url=http://ff7.ocremix.org/tracks/|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=ff7.ocremix.org|archive-date=2012-10-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B9DrZSS0?url=http://ff7.ocremix.org/tracks/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2013年，“《爱丽丝主题曲》在《Classic FM》殿堂中排名第三。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Classic FM's Hall of Fame|url=https://halloffame.classicfm.com/2013/chart/|accessdate=2020-07-05|last=Radio|first=Global|work=Classic FM's Hall of Fame|language=en}}</ref>

== 评价 ==
爱丽丝得到了评论家的总体好评。《[[GamesTM|GamesTM]]》称她为“游戏界的传奇”。<ref name=":2" />RPGamer的Stuart Hoggan认为，尽管爱丽丝“代表处境艰难的少女”，但她“打破了人格的桎梏，”拥有“令人敬畏的勇气。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=RPGamer - Editorials - Damsels and Distress?|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080512021014/http://www.rpgamer.com/editor/2007/q2/061107sh.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2008-05-12|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>2007年，由于她的死亡场面以及美丽的外表和个性，她被《Tom's Games》列入电子游戏史上前50名最伟大的女性角色之列。<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|title=The 50 Greatest Female Characters in Video Game History {{!}} Tom's Games|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120114601/http://www.tomsgames.com/us/2007/02/20/the_50_greatest_female_characters_in_the_history_of_video_games/page9.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2008-01-20|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>同年，她在《[[電擊PlayStation|電擊PlayStation]]》有关原版PlayStation的回顾性奖项中被评为有史以来第五好的人物。<ref>{{Citation|title=Nomura Talks FFXIII - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/22/nomura-talks-ffxiii|accessdate=2020-07-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609085636/https://www.ign.com/articles/2007/11/22/nomura-talks-ffxiii|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]在《最终幻想VII》的顶级角色列表中将她排在第二位，比游戏的主角克劳德高出一位。<ref>{{Citation|title=Final Fantasy VII: Top 10 Characters - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/03/25/final-fantasy-vii-top-10-characters|accessdate=2020-07-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610023737/https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/03/25/final-fantasy-vii-top-10-characters|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]在2010年将她列为“不属于您的女人”名单的首位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/c/gametrailers|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2019-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719110621/https://www.youtube.com/c/gametrailers|dead-url=no}}</ref> GameZone的Heath Hooker在2012年的《最终幻想》角色排行榜中将爱丽丝排在第五位，并写道：“不仅在《最终幻想》系列中，而且在视频游戏历史上，爱丽丝都成为了偶像。” <ref>{{Cite web|title=Top 10 Final Fantasy Characters|url=https://www.gamezone.com/originals/top-10-final-fantasy-characters/|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2012-05-04|last=Hooker|first=Heath|work=GameZone|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190601213038/https://www.gamezone.com/originals/top-10-final-fantasy-characters/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她与克劳德的关系也收到了积极的评价，其中包括在IGN的有关最佳视频游戏恋情的文章中列出了两人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Top 10 Tuesday: Best Videogame Romances - PS2 Feature at IGN|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629123257/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/688/688837p1.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2011-06-29|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

该角色在游戏玩家中很受欢迎，尤其是日本玩家和《最终幻想》系列的粉丝。她被包括在[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]的大多数“角色大战”竞赛中，尽管爱丽丝每次仅能进行几轮。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameFAQs - Summer 2002: "The Great GameFAQs Character Battle"|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929141251/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/c02sum|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2007-09-29|work=web.archive.org}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=GameFAQs Contests - GameFAQs|url=https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/features/contest/c03sum|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=gamefaqs.gamespot.com|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706122351/https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/features/contest/c03sum|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=GameFAQs Contests - GameFAQs|url=https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/features/contest/cb5|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=gamefaqs.gamespot.com|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705211958/https://gamefaqs.gamespot.com/features/contest/cb5|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年，《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》读者将爱丽丝评选为第24佳电子游戏角色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Snake Beats Mario, Is Coolest Video Game Character Ever|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622072101/http://www.1up.com/news/snake-beats-mario-coolest-video|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2011-06-22|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>2013年，爱丽丝在史克威尔艾尼克斯的官方民意调查中被票选为第二最受欢迎的女性《最终幻想》角色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Square Enix Poll: Favorite Female Final Fantasy Character|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2013-01-17/square-enix-poll/favorite-female-final-fantasy-character|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=Anime News Network|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190531063613/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2013-01-17/square-enix-poll/favorite-female-final-fantasy-character|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，《Complex》杂志将她列为有史以来第七大最终幻想角色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The 20 Greatest Final Fantasy Characters of All Time|url=https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2013/10/greatest-final-fantasy-characters-all-time/|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=Complex|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200524042144/https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2013/10/greatest-final-fantasy-characters-all-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年，日本广播公司[[日本廣播協會|NHK]]对所有《最终幻想》系列进行了全球性但主要针对日本的调查。爱丽丝排名第三，仅次于第一名克劳德和第二名優娜（《最终幻想X》）。因此，爱丽丝分别位居第二最受欢迎的女性角色和《最终幻想VII》角色。<ref>{{Cite web|title=結果発表｜全ファイナルファンタジー大投票｜NHK|url=https://www.nhk.or.jp/anime/ff/ranking/index.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|last=日本放送協会|work=結果発表｜全ファイナルファンタジー大投票｜NHK|language=ja|archive-date=2020-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200313204656/https://www.nhk.or.jp/anime/ff/ranking/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

重制版中，爱丽丝角色在整个故事中的关心他人的程度和角色的发展受到了Siliconera的称赞。 尽管批评缺少了做错了事情来平衡角色表现的事件，但Siliconera仍然很喜欢她在古留根尾场景的表现，该网站还非常喜欢她与其他成员互动的方式。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy VII Remake’s Aerith Is Kind and Even More Enigmatic|url=https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-vii-remakes-aerith-remains-kind-and-appropriately-enigmatic/|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2020-04-15|work=Siliconera|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427070842/https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-vii-remakes-aerith-remains-kind-and-appropriately-enigmatic/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

