《最终幻想VII》中爱丽丝的死亡获得了相当多的关注。根据[[GamesTM|GamesTM]]的说法，她的死帮助确立了《最终幻想VII》的知名度。<ref name=":2" />玩家在各种留言板和博客上讲述了那个场景所造成的情感影响。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameSpy: Case File 28: Is Square Enix milking the Final Fantasy VII franchise? - Page 2|url=http://www.gamespy.com/articles/551/551742p2.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.gamespy.com|archive-date=2007-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071105213020/http://www.gamespy.com/articles/551/551742p2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>粉丝们向北濑佳范提交了请愿书，要求将她复活。<ref name=":2" />[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]将她的死亡视为电子游戏历史上第十大电影时刻，<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameSpy:|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011003254/http://www.gamespy.com/articles/771/771937p4.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2007-10-11|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>而其读者则将其评为第二大电影时刻。<ref>{{Cite web|title=GameSpy: Readers' Choice Top 10 Most Cinematic Moments in Gaming - Page 5|url=http://www.gamespy.com/articles/798/798722p5.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=www.gamespy.com|archive-date=2007-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071015052721/http://www.gamespy.com/articles/798/798722p5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[GamePro|GamePro]]认为她的死亡场景是所有游戏场景中最深刻的。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Feature : The 55 Greatest Moments in Gaming (page 9 of 9) [Domestic] - from GamePro.com|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913213635/http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/75048/the-55-greatest-moments-in-gaming-page-9-of-9/|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2008-09-13|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>Tom's Games称该场景为“最终幻想系列中，甚至包括其他任何游戏中，最有力和令人难忘的场景之一。” <ref name=":4" />《Edge》将她的死亡称为《最终幻想VII》的“戏剧化的顶峰”，并表示通过《最终幻想VII补完计划》重新介绍她“可以说破坏了这一伟大时刻。”<ref>{{Cite journal|title="Final Frontiers"|author=Future plc|url=|journal=Edge|issue=177|doi=|others=|year=July 2007|volume=|page=72-79|pmid=}}</ref> 2005年，《[[电子游戏月刊|电子游戏月刊]]》在其“十个最重要的游戏列表”中将《最终幻想VII》列为第六名，并指出如果没有这款游戏，“爱丽丝不会死，玩家也不会知道怎么学会哭。”<ref>{{Cite web|title=Reading Electronic Gaming Monthly|url=https://readingegm.tumblr.com/post/120062073745/egm-187-the-10-most-important-games-as-of-2005|accessdate=2020-07-05|work=Reading Electronic Gaming Monthly|archive-date=2020-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200707110258/https://readingegm.tumblr.com/post/120062073745/egm-187-the-10-most-important-games-as-of-2005|dead-url=no}}</ref>ScrewAttack将爱丽丝之死放到了他们的前10大“ OMGWTF”时刻，称其为电子游戏历史上“最动人的时刻”之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gametrailers.com - ScrewAttack - Top 10 OMGWTF Moments|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080729185045/http://www.gametrailers.com/player/36111.html|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2008-07-29|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>2011年，IGN在其“电子游戏场景排名”中，将她的死亡场景排名第一。<ref>{{Citation|title=Top 100 Unforgettable Video Game Moments - IGN.com|url=https://www.ign.com/lists/top-100-video-game-moments|accessdate=2020-07-05|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802234752/https://www.ign.com/lists/top-100-video-game-moments|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年，《[[PlayStation官方杂志－英国|PlayStation官方杂志 - 英国]]》将其列入十大最感人的PlayStation时刻之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The 10 most emotional PlayStation moments - Page 5 of 10 {{!}} Uncategorized {{!}} Official PlayStation Magazine|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102220501/http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/2012/06/12/the-10-most-emotional-playstation-moments/5/#gallery-top|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2013-11-02|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>在她和主角克劳德之间，死亡也被认为是不幸爱情故事的决定性时刻。<ref>{{Cite book|title=The History of the Kiss: The Birth of Popular Culture, Semiotics and Popular Culture|last=Danesi|first=|publisher=Palgrave Macmillan|year=2013|isbn=978-1-137-37683-1|location=|pages=50-51}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Ten Greatest Romances in Gaming History|url=https://www.technobuffalo.com/the-ten-greatest-romances-in-gaming-history|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2011-04-29|work=TechnoBuffalo|archive-date=2020-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705104001/https://www.technobuffalo.com/the-ten-greatest-romances-in-gaming-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布莱恩·泰勒（Brian Taylor）为《Kill Screen》撰写文章，描述了一个“粉丝理论”的行动，即这些粉丝如何使爱丽丝复活或防止其死亡。他将这些努力与以说服[[查尔斯·狄更斯|查尔斯·狄更斯]]不要让《[[老古玩店|老古玩店]]》的可爱主角耐尔在书的结尾处死的写信运动进行了比较。泰勒认为，讨论这些“粉丝理论”并剖析游戏代码以对其进行测试的行为，是游戏体验的有效而重要的部分。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Brian Taylor » Archive » Save Aeris – How Can We Be Moved by the Fate of Aeris Gainsborough (Kill Screen)|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140801034737/http://btphotographer.com/blog/2011/09/04/save-aeris-how-can-we-be-moved-by-the-fate-of-aeris-gainsborough-kill-screen/|accessdate=2020-07-05|date=2014-08-01|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>

